# 🔢 Value Counter

A simple interactive counter built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript — one of my first hands-on projects while learning web development.

🔗 **Live Demo:** [clever-sunburst-a5eb32.netlify.app](https://clever-sunburst-a5eb32.netlify.app)

---

## 📌 About

This is a beginner project I built while learning HTML and JavaScript. It demonstrates basic DOM manipulation — clicking buttons updates the displayed value in real time.

---

## ✨ Features

- ➕ Increment the counter
- ➖ Decrement the counter
- 🔢 Live value display that updates instantly

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript

---

## 🚀 Run Locally

No setup needed — just open the file in a browser.

